Package: systest
Architecture: all
Depends: python3.8, ${misc:Depends}
Description: System test framework for Behave-based suites
  Provides a CLI to run behavioral system test suites organized by feature areas
  and Gherkin .feature files. Enforces a structured suite layout with step
  definitions and support modules, and supports execution of full suites,
  feature areas, specific feature files, or individual scenarios.
